Murray & Roberts to Report Loss from Discontinued Operations in Full Year

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-08-19T11:31:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-19/murray-roberts-to-report-loss-from-discontinued-operations-in-full-year.html
Murray and Robert Holdings Ltd.
expects to record a diluted loss per share of 5.75 rand to 6.15
rand for the year through June after accounting for the loss
from discontinued operations, it said in an updated trading
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  